high_descs: Walk across the room to the shelf, turn right, walk until there is a counter on your left, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the dirty pan from the counter.
Turn around, walk forward one step, then turn left and walk until you get to the sink.
Place the pan in the sink, rinse it off, then pick it back up.
Turn around, then turn to the cabinet beside the oven.
Open the cabinet and place the pan inside.
anns.task_desc: Clean the dirty pan and put it away.

high_descs: Walk ahead and veer right to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the dirty pan on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Turn left and look at the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the pot in the cabinet under the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean pan in a cabinet.

high_descs: Go to the counter left of the stove
